{"id":76505,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/06/转载国务院办公厅关于征地拆迁紧急通知（全文）/","date":"2010-06-05T04:32:31Z","modified":"2010-06-05T13:08:39Z","title":"梅春来律师：国务院办公厅关于征地拆迁紧急通知（全文附图）","content":"<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/06/4c808cbdg8800f7282820690.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-76613\" title=\"4c808cbdg8800f7282820&amp;690\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/06/4c808cbdg8800f7282820690.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"508\" height=\"690\" /></a><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/06/4c808cbdg8800f8966178690.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-76614\" title=\"4c808cbdg8800f8966178&amp;690\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/06/4c808cbdg8800f8966178690.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"455\" height=\"690\" /></a><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/06/4c808cbdg8800f95bfd30690.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-76615\" title=\"4c808cbdg8800f95bfd30&amp;690\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/06/4c808cbdg8800f95bfd30690.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"456\" height=\"690\" /></a></p>\n<p>对采取停水、停电、阻断交通等野蛮手段逼迫搬迁，以及采取“株连式<strong>拆迁</strong>”和“突击<strong>拆迁</strong>”等方式违法<strong>强制拆迁</strong>的，要严格追究有关责任单位和责任人的责任。因<strong>暴力拆迁</strong>和<strong>征地</strong>造成人员伤亡或严重财产损失的，公安机关要加大办案力度，尽快查清事实，依法严厉惩处犯罪 &#8230; 省、自治区、直辖市人民政府要加强对<strong>征地拆迁</strong>工作的管理和监督，切实加强对<strong>征地拆迁</strong>规模的总量调控，防止和纠正大拆大建。市、县人民政府对<strong>征地拆迁</strong>管理工作负总责，要明确政府分管负责人的责任，对出现<strong>群体性事件</strong>的，市、县人民政府主要负责人要亲临 &#8230;</p>\n<p>More here:<br />\n<a title=\"[转载]国务院办公厅关于征地拆迁紧急通知（全文）_被征地户_新浪博客\" href=\"http://blog.sina.com.cn/s/blog_63cd4d8a0100iugz.html\" target=\"_blank\">[转载]国务院办公厅关于征地拆迁紧急通知（全文）_被征地户_新浪博客</a></p>\n","author":114,"categories":[20534],"tags":[8937,9094,9377]}